Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.05,0:00:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再當乙HiME了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.25,0:00:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再使用\N乙HiME的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.23,0:00:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領，卡迪亞來信了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，妳慢著！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.36,0:01:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將彼此重疊的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖進記憶深處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟昨天不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.63,0:01:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我就站在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降臨而下的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔地包容一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我訴說著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「守護」的真正意義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾度仰望無限寬闊的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘不了 那一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法再回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:02:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量滿溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱切地 強烈地 勇猛地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在沒有光芒的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能感覺到聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你能發現我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第20話 不要叫我妮依娜\N不過真是意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到卡迪亞竟然主動低頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說國際情勢\N已經十分危險了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟著她們不管好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，要談等回來再說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你們看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亞，聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然阿爾泰的小鬼\N掌握了加爾德羅貝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要不擇手段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人擁有的科學力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必也可以\N助我卡迪亞的繁榮一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以請教一件事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人是不會忘記的民族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦我們下手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必他們會反抗我卡迪亞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就是群烏合之是罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳只要服從我的命令便可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了，皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙，這樣太失禮了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看看這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長閣下幾時變得會把責任\N轉嫁到新上任的同事身上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，自己負責嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是大人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之，現在的問題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用妳多說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我，五柱之一的“冰雪的銀水晶”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以加爾德羅貝學園長之名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向愛瑞斯共和國請求協助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長，很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,議會還在爭論這件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前與議會工作一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先收集著情報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝遭到不當佔領
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想馬上趕過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後讓那個凪小鬼叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在愛瑞斯要是輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許就會出現親阿爾泰的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是陣營因此瓦解的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.87,0:05:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此瓦解的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳笑這麼多會死的啦，小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說愛莉卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想在這裡待到幾時？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能永遠待在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣或許也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的乙HiME真祖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要做那種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說女武神部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不需勞動父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我的手已經黑透了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓我可愛的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再覺得難過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮依娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別再叫我妮依娜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經15歲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也成為Meister了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再用叫小孩子的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也算是父親的悲裒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，等會見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如情報所示呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，似乎是把孤兒\N或綁架來的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,培養成殺手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真噁心的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙是\N擁立第一公子的餘孽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要留活口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是碎片擦過而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把槍放下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮…娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳很害怕對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙大大的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…就是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對父親來說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠都是當年的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託…看看我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME的力量竟是那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠生出GEM的母體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須是過去曾為乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來生兒育子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為母親的女性身體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得做到那種程度不可嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被提醒過很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成為乙HiME是很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼笨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一樣很笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我比較笨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我比較笨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我害的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能瞭解更多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯也不會死…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋的事情也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是弄錯一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳現在還說這幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳笨又老是犯錯\N不已經是常態了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白不會懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我重要的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這種好像只有妳受傷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵她？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的，我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王\N一定會成為一個優秀的王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…必須活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是為了\N因我而捨棄性命的葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我吻妳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不可以死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認證啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是妳的乙HiME之力…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要，我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再成為乙HiME了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠待在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦，妳安分點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想…想把我們消化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是\N叫賈巴爾的玩意兒肚子裡耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫…叫我跳？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怪的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很怪呢，真白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得，像個笨蛋一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就說討厭乙HiME了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子被？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:14:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑰麗的…縞…瑪瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡迪亞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的研究成果被…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是中途入學的女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到真白女王也在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼要這麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister竟然做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村人做了什麼壞事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人希望我這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是命令，妳什麼都肯做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將性命交給主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服從主人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是乙HiME的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滅火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人，快來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯歐他…魯歐他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白，那個人拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的人，來幫…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在發什麼呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡我來處理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要是有空的話，這個給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還啊，快滅火去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯歐，出個聲音啊，魯歐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯歐，振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭…領
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油，別擔心，我馬上救你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯歐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:15:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,REM的資料被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…好個阿格斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉德，你指揮男人們滅火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伽爾\N去確認研究室受害的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴因負責搬運傷患
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯曼率領女人們進行急救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別怕，黑色山谷的子民們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們團結
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點程度的考驗不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家借我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面寫著\N可以成為阿爾泰的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？可以成為Meister嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說報酬可以隨意索取
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，請在文件上填上必要資料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要轉告王少校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？急事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來總算稍微穩定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可真的累到翻了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳很拼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像是第一次\N看到拼命做事的真白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被妳稱讚也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯歐似乎得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此向妳道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領，乙HiME是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直覺得乙HiME是正義之士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我很排斥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我一旦遇到緊急狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是又變成了乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出這麼過份的事的\N也是乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我又是因為變成乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能救出魯歐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外什麼也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是好呢？還是不好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量沒有好壞之分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有力量只會死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是支配這個世界的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人們才會追求乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求由科學所生出的巨大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了活下去，為了成就事物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也一樣吧？愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊，我來接妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起請在這裡生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不會讓別人\N碰靜留姊姊一根汗毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以告訴我一件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾，已經被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在被關在風華宮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要執行第一個任務了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視任務成果而定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定可以再得到獎賞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真要請妳好好加油呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到連妳都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有所不滿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，很讓人放心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千繪·海拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是叫古風琴的\N上個時代的科學結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要實現我跟謝爾蓋的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要這玩意兒的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不覺得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝封鎖地球時代的科學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為乙HiME的英靈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保住薄皮一般的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓這一切結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且想要找回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類最閃耀的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種懷念的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不可能這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們就是渴望古風琴之力的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.63,0:22:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:22:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.46,0:23:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.86,0:23:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要找回人類最閃耀的時代\N（白色公主，覺醒之時）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.59,0:23:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心話呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.66,0:23:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣比較好玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事啦，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.33,0:23:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不該順應情勢\N跟你定下契約的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.66,0:23:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算理解愛莉卡的辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.80,0:23:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳這什麼意思？
